Package: reddPrec
Title: Reconstruction of Daily Data - Precipitation
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Roberto", "Serrano-Notivoli", , "roberto.serrano@unizar.es", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7663-1202"))
Description: Applies quality control to daily precipitation observations; 
    reconstructs the original series by estimating precipitation in missing values; and 
    creates gridded datasets of daily precipitation.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://rsnotivoli.github.io/reddPrec/, https://github.com/rsnotivoli/reddPrec
BugReports: https://github.com/rsnotivoli/reddPrec/issues
Imports: terra, stats, foreach, doParallel, reshape, qmap
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
